<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/474032e7g9ac61b12ed04" TARGET="_blank"><img NAME="image_operate_84501296078544216" SRC="http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/474032e7g9ac61b12ed04&amp;690" WIDTH="501" HEIGHT="334" /></A><br />
