<p><br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/474032e7g9ac61bf93c67" TARGET="_blank"><img NAME="image_operate_65381296078559698" SRC="http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/474032e7g9ac61bf93c67&amp;690" WIDTH="372" HEIGHT="499" /></A><br />
