<p><br />
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/474032e7g9ac6203d869e" TARGET="_blank"><img NAME="image_operate_80031296078341935" SRC="http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/474032e7g9ac6203d869e&amp;690" WIDTH="499" HEIGHT="333" /></A></P>
